rental.headline: Spacious courtyard apartment
rental.description:
Nestled in a private, leafy enclave of prestigious St Ives, Eden apartments combine refined luxury with the best of contemporary living. Architect designed, they feature harmoniously proportioned spaces, integrated outdoor living and beautiful landscaped vistas.
APARTMENT
Beautifully crafted interiors and masterful design combine to create private, elegant spaces. Flexible living area flow seamlessly to outdoor entertaining area. This particular apartment enjoys a private courtyard and grassed area.
Elegant kitchen with discreet soft closing cabinetry and designer finishes in natural, muted tones complement these stylish interiors without dominating. Premium collection appliances, caesarstone bench top, glass splash back and polyurethane cabinetry.
Each bedroom is generously proportioned and includes built in wardrobes. The master bedroom includes a designer ensuite. The main bathroom and ensuite are both luxuriously appointed with quality fittings, frameless glass screens and fully tiled with a limestone feature wall.
Also includes; ducted air conditioning, security access, secure private storage and secure parking.
Set in a quiet tree lined street in landscaped gardens with majestic mature trees, it is an oasis of serene luxury.
These apartments will bring new level of refinement and sophistication to apartment living in St Ives - with Eden certain to become the standard against which all other apartments will be measured.
LOCATION
St Ives is one of the Upper North Shore's most sought after suburbs. Destination shopping, prestigious schools, recreation facilities and multiple modes of transport are all within easy reach.
Eden apartments are only a short stroll to St Ives shopping centre, where you'll find: Woolworths, Harris Farm, wonderful cafes, travel centre, homewares, clothing and medical suites.
Offering an ideal lifestyle in a picture perfect setting and with easy access to national parks, business precincts and shops, it's no surprise that St Ives is one of the North Shore's most desirable suburbs.

rental.headline: Grand Celebrity Residence
rental.description:
A world class residence with exceptional design pedigree situated in Sydney's most exclusive harbour front enclave.
This is an outstanding home where uncompromising design by award winning architects Burley Katon Halliday (BKH) and interiors by highly acclaimed Tobias Partners have created the ultimate in luxury living.
There are four levels of living all beautifully designed to showcase the spectacular harbour views. A grand formal entrance provides an inviting welcome and hints to the outstanding beauty and design within. From here it leads to an opulent entertainers retreat or formal living area, adjoining this is a handsome study, which is separated by custom joinery and includes an integrated open fireplace. The perfect winter retreat.
There is a separate informal living area and an expansive dining area which seamlessly extend to beautiful terraced outdoor areas. A gourmet kitchen featuring custom marble benches, imported veneer cabinetry, professional standard appliances, a large walk-in pantry and wine cellar.
The bedroom wing comprises four double bedrooms each with their own ensuite and built in storage. The master suite is a luxurious retreat which opens on to a private terrace overlooking the harbour. It has an exquisite dressing room, finished in marble, glass and travertine, the ensuite with an opulent stand alone bath.
There is a separate fully self-contained level, with a kitchen, bathroom, separate rumpus room, ideal for in-law accommodation or live in help.
Set in beautifully landscaped gardens, with an extensive level backyard and fully automated watering system. A designer in-ground salt water, heated pool with aqua jets and water features complements this exquisite setting.
There is parking for four vehicles in a lock-up garage plus additional guest parking.
Some of the other many features are; a home intelligence system, zoned ducted reverse cycle air conditioning and audio system, internal lift and designer lighting throughout.
This is a very private and tranquil home offering the ultimate in luxury living.
